{"tid":1840461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何防止大陸死蝗蟲走數？","createTime":"2020-01-24T23:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T09:07:13.000Z","uid":195944,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c68a507e57fea00f2c7411c5200e1b3c20ede954","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:17:03.000Z","msg":"個兩個確診咗武漢肺炎嘅一聽到嘅死武漢蟲一聽到要俾咁貴醫療費就走佬<br />\n<br />\n我想問 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醫管局如何防止佢地走數？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家唔係咩人唔人道 要救咗人先啲懶係高尚嘅概念<br />\n人梗係要救 但點樣要病人負返責任？<br />\n<br />\n希望有記者可以問膠把升 無始笑 陳漢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e39b97d7867bdb0196df5fef2f7f3a5a5f6cc69","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:24:12.000Z","msg":"我好愛蟈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但大陸蟲真係會咁做<br />\n<br />\n非本地居民5年走數逾2.3億強國人藉詞醫療失誤做「院霸」<br />\n<br />\n醫管局 政府做過啲咩改善依個問題？"},{"pid":"6baeed4f2cb8ff4eca2a2ea733f1d0c45ef76d14","tid":1840461,"uid":268516,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:26:36.000Z","msg":"學支那咁<br />\n乜都先俾咗錢先"},{"pid":"4d362a448093d268f24649b5860749e640c170db","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:27:46.000Z","msg":"投訴師 出黎啦！<br />\n<br />\n去申訴專員公署問下！<br />\n<br />\n睇下有無人失職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a7835a6987420ae2ef089e32f8367895d0dd54","tid":1840461,"uid":292987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:28:47.000Z","msg":"港共政府唔會理 甚至創造機會俾佢地走數<br />\n係咁奶 奶到盡"},{"pid":"f1f5146f8184bb3d363b5d0a553319f5b8c60af7","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6baeed4f2cb8ff4eca2a2ea733f1d0c45ef76d14","tid":1840461,"uid":268516,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:26:36.000Z","msg":"學支那咁<br />\n乜都先俾咗錢先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:29:36.000Z","msg":"奶共政府會閪咁做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde829cb7ba9ff40ee0b91bf51509d585c438789","tid":1840461,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1f5146f8184bb3d363b5d0a553319f5b8c60af7","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6baeed4f2cb8ff4eca2a2ea733f1d0c45ef76d14","tid":1840461,"uid":268516,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:26:36.000Z","msg":"學支那咁<br />\n乜都先俾咗錢先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:29:36.000Z","msg":"奶共政府會閪咁做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:32:40.000Z","msg":"自己去收咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeaeda5d3a49f96e44bef1b3d53f599634bf5bcf","tid":1840461,"uid":138981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:32:58.000Z","msg":"救又死唔救又死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救就拖數+喺醫院傳播病毒+辛苦晒醫護人員<br />\n唔救就通街走周圍傳染<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd88fac19d7bdf9e6d921265e2e24be256ef1921","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:34:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-04/03/33848.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2019-04%2F03%2F33848.html&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=c0374112\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-04/03/33848.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一名內地婦人被揭在港遇車禍後，享用公立醫院治療，但一直「走數」，沒有交治療費用，期間曾住過兩間醫院，被醫管局追討合共617萬元欠款，原來此案只是冰山一角，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始承認，醫管局每年平均都要花400萬元追數，當中包括法律費用和其他開支。<br />\n<br />\n現時包括內地人在內的非合資格人士，使用本港公立醫療服務，須繳付醫療費用，金額以收回成本原則釐定。陳肇始表示，在17/18財政年度，每宗「走數」個案平均拖欠14500元，<span style=\"color: red;\">最大宗「走數」個案拖欠達470萬元</span>，創五年新高。<br />\n<br />\n綜合五個財政年度看，非合資格人士拖欠治療費用，平均拖欠超過100日，最嚴重個案拖欠1210日，即大約三年零四個月。<br />\n<br />\n病人出院時，醫管局會發出終結賬單，或將賬單寄給病人。<span style=\"color: red;\">若病人出院後仍未繳清費用，醫管局會致電和寄出月結單提醒，如病人在指定時間內仍未付清費用，醫管局會徵收行政費，另外亦會採取適當法律行動追收欠款</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但也有個案要撇賬，在17/18年度，平均撇賬金額達7700元，最大宗撇賬要170萬元，在14/15年度，最大宗撇賬更要450萬元，平均撇賬金額約9800元。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始表示，除非是緊急情況，非符合資格人士入院時須繳付按金，但非符合資格人士一般都是在緊急情況下入院，假若這些住院個案較嚴重，而需要留醫，一般都要接受較長時間治療，因此個別撇賬個案金額較高。"},{"pid":"0eda0e02686bb2dd596b8c8c481246b113570dac","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:36:43.000Z","msg":"如來每年要花四百萬追數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bdae126b0e8bec23440ba01e5ecc3387395636","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:37:20.000Z","msg":"武漢人：我睇到醫生係我本事 點解要俾錢？"},{"pid":"267433e1ee434c206f3811b04224b5a27b66f492","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:41:18.000Z","msg":"但也有個案要撇賬，在17/18年度，平均撇賬金額達7700元，最大宗撇賬要170萬元，在14/15年度，最大宗撇賬更要450萬元，平均撇賬金額約9800元。<br />\n<br />\n要求醫管局公開詳細資料 <br />\n希望每區區議員可以幫手<br />\n立法會議員 求下你地要醫管局公開實情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下邊啲人種係走數常客<br />\n點解追唔返<br />\n佢地唔諗方法 就等市民議員諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d9473ceba446617b735dcd7e127dd11aab5834","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:44:08.000Z","msg":"問下醫管局 醫護人員加班有無ot費？<br />\n點解克警咁易批？ 醫護人員就好似乞衣咁乞都無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8669d6a420aeafd6b0bccef134c16fec65275cda","tid":1840461,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:49:06.000Z","msg":"就唔找數事小，引致社區爆發，再感染香港醫護人員，就真係罪不可恕"},{"pid":"8d94e6f4786eed798bb977cdb1ef585cdc91026a","tid":1840461,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8669d6a420aeafd6b0bccef134c16fec65275cda","tid":1840461,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:49:06.000Z","msg":"就唔找數事小，引致社區爆發，再感染香港醫護人員，就真係罪不可恕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:57:34.000Z","msg":"知可以走，大把人嚟睇"},{"pid":"3b97ebe65e5b31c607299f6fe2e7379f8078d1b8","tid":1840461,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:59:21.000Z","msg":"打電話 寄信喎<br />\n<br />\n醫管局 你連人地住邊都唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9068b93c911703d24dc1b52f9a79d4e65be5acfa","tid":1840461,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:02:21.000Z","msg":"我有個更好嘅主意<br />\n<br />\n點解唔即刻槍斃然後火化呢"},{"pid":"aaaa5d7a5d4a00d56637612514816a849fced127","tid":1840461,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d94e6f4786eed798bb977cdb1ef585cdc91026a","tid":1840461,"uid":